*** Second '''Witness Stack''': The witness data corresponding to the second input.
**** Item count for the second '''Witness Stack''' <code>03</code>: serialization artifact, two or more Witness Items indicate a script path spend.
**** First '''Witness Item'''
***** '''Length of the first Witness Item''' <code>40</code>: 64 bytes indicate a signature
